      "content": "Your symptoms of sharp, migrating stomach pain, especially localized to the bottom right with pain on movement, could indicate appendicitis and require immediate medical attention. Please do not take ibuprofen if you might have an appendiceal issue, as it can mask symptoms, or take too many painkillers without first seeing a doctor. You should stop taking anything at home and go to the emergency room or call emergency services right away.",
